  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 14 (Spell Level 7)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 20</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 31 | <b>Successes:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 19 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 39</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You make a bite-like touch attack against the target (a nonproficiency penalty may apply), forcing a cursed seal onto its body and granting it the Cursed Seal template with you as its origin, and the Cursed Seal Level 1 ability (p342). Ths subject is initially unwilling, and will gain a level adjustment (see template). The subject must make one Fortitude save (DC 15) per day for ten days. If they fail two in a row, they die.<br><br>You suffer 2 negative levels and must make a Fortitude save (DC 23) after 24 hours. If it succeeds, the negative levels are cured. If not, they become permanent. Once per day per subject, you can use a gaze attack against subjects carrying 'your' cursed seal to have various effects (see Cursed Seal Template).</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
